OL,3,CHeat alerts issued ahead of busy
OL,4,Ctravel weekend
OL,6,FHeat alerts are in place across parts
OL,7,Fof England, with officials warning
OL,8,Fthat temperatures are likely have an
OL,9,Fimpact on health ahead of one of the
OL,10,Fbusiest travel weekends of the year.
OL,12,FThe yellow heat health alerts issued
OL,13,Ffor the East Midlands, East of
OL,14,FEngland, London, South East, South
OL,15,FWest and West Midlands are in place
OL,16,Ffrom 9am on Friday until 9am on Sunday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
