OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1784918934
OL,3,CHeat alerts issued ahead of busy
OL,4,Ctravel weekend
OL,6,FTemperatures in the affected areas are
OL,7,Fforecast to reach mid to high 20s,
OL,8,Fwith a high of 30C a possibility, as
OL,9,Fmuch of the country continues to
OL,10,Fexperience a prolonged period of dry,
OL,11,Fwarm weather.
OL,13,FThe heat alerts are in place at the
OL,14,Fbeginning of a stretch in which
OL,15,Fmillions of motorists are expected to
OL,16,Ftake to the roads for summer getaways.
OL,18,FThe AA said around 6.3 million drivers
OL,19,Fare planning a road trip of more than
OL,20,F100 miles between Friday and Thursday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
