OL,3,CHeat alerts issued ahead of busy
OL,4,Ctravel weekend
OL,6,FThe Port of Dover is expecting another
OL,7,Fbusy weekend but has worked to smooth
OL,8,Fany delays caused by new EU border
OL,9,Fchecks.
OL,11,FThe heat health warning from the UK
OL,12,FHealth Security Agency (UKHSA) comes
OL,13,Fas drought was declared in North Wales
OL,14,Fand the Upper Severn, following record
OL,15,Fdry conditions, heatwaves, wildfires
OL,16,Fand dwindling rivers.
OL,18,FIt is the first part of the UK to
OL,19,Fdeclare drought status amid a summer
OL,20,Fof record-breaking heatwaves.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
