CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1784918934
OL,3,CHeat alerts issued ahead of busy
OL,4,Ctravel weekend
OL,6,FMany parts of England are in prolonged
OL,7,Fdry weather status as the country has
OL,8,Freceived just 3% of its average July
OL,9,Frainfall, with hosepipe bans in place
OL,10,Ffor 23 million customers and suppliers
OL,11,Fwarning they may stay in place all
OL,12,Fsummer.
OL,14,FWildfires have been raging in a number
OL,15,Fof places in England, while Scotland
OL,16,Fhas also been hit by a major wildfire
OL,17,Fin the Cairngorms, and in the Republic
OL,18,Fof Ireland, a nationwide hosepipe ban
OL,19,Fis in place in response to the dry
OL,20,Fconditions.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
