OL,3,CHeat alerts issued ahead of busy
OL,4,Ctravel weekend
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FThis summer's dry conditions follow
OL,12,Flast year's drought summer, as the UK
OL,13,Fincreasingly faces more extreme
OL,14,Fweather fuelled by human-caused
OL,15,Fclimate change, mostly from burning
OL,16,Ffossil fuels.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/7
