CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1784918934
OL,3,CHeat alerts issued ahead of busy
OL,4,Ctravel weekend
OL,6,FThe Met Office said temperatures could
OL,7,Freach 30C in parts of South East
OL,8,FEngland on Friday while parts of
OL,9,FScotland and Northern Ireland will see
OL,10,Fpatches of cloud.
OL,12,FForecaster Craig Snell said outbreaks
OL,13,Fof rain will move southwards on
OL,14,FSaturday, spreading from Scotland and
OL,15,FNorthern Ireland into northern England
OL,16,Fand parts of Wales.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/7
