OL,3,CHeat alerts issued ahead of busy
OL,4,Ctravel weekend
OL,6,FBy Sunday, temperatures are expected
OL,7,Fto turn "fresher" across much of the
OL,8,FUK, with rain possible in "areas that
OL,9,Fhaven't seen much" over the past few
OL,10,Fweeks, he added.
